---
name: Cloudability API Reference
description: Cloudability V3 API endpoints, auth methods, and US base URL for Siemens FinOps integration
type: reference
---
- Base URL: https://api.cloudability.com (US — NOT EU)
- Auth: Basic Auth with API key as username, empty password
- Date params: `start_date` and `end_date` (NOT `start`/`end`)
- Response field: `results` array (NOT `result`)
- Dimension for vendor: `vendor` (NOT `vendor_name`). Values: "Amazon", "Azure"
- Sort parameter does NOT work with v3 cost reports — sort client-side
- `/v3/rightsizing` returns 404 — endpoint not available with Basic Auth key
- `usage_hours` metric with `category4==Compute` filter returns 0 results
- Key working endpoints: /v3/reporting/cost/run
- Environment ID: f2ee502f-2f35-45c1-8bc5-7d4748f637b6 (for UI reference only)
